<h3>Novatorix admin panel options</h3>
<ul><h4>'General' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Select your preferred color scheme.</li>
		<li>URL to your logo.</li>		
		<li>Enter your header slogan or you can select select widget 'Homepage slogan'.</li>		
		<li>Page that will show Blog posts.</li>				
		<li>Exclude Pages.</li>						
		<li>Exclude Blog Categories.</li>								
		<li>Enable breadcrumbs</li>
		<li>Tracking Code (e.g. Google Analytics). The code will be added to the footer of each pages.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>


<ul><h4>'Homepage 3 Columns' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Enter 3 columns title, url, image url and description or you can select select widgets 'Homepage column 1', 'Homepage column 2' and 'Homepage column 3'.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

<ul><h4>'Homepage 4 Columns' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Enter 4 columns title and description.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

<ul><h4>'Homepage slider' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Please enter how many images to show in homepage slider. Note: click 'Save changes' and after you will instert images and descrtption.</li>
		<li>Select slider: Nivo slider, Piecemaker 3D slider or use static image. If you will select static image, please enter 'Static Image URL' and 'Static Go To URL' (optional).</li>
		<li>Upload all images into your theme folder /novatorix/scripts/piecemaker/images/ and enter only image name (e.g. image1.jpg).</li>
		<li>Enter 'Headline', 'Description' for all images. Required is only 'Image name', 'Headline' and 'Description' are optional.</li>
		<li>Use a lot of slider options like Image Width, Image Height, Segments, Tween Type, etc.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

<ul><h4>'Portfolio' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Choose the number of items you want to display on your Portfolio Gallery view Pages. In Portfolio full view will show default number from 'Reading Settings' => (http://www.yoursite.com/wp-admin/options-reading.php)</li>
		<li>Assign Portfolio Page to a Category. Must be selected page templates for portfolio already when you will create pages.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

<ul><h4>'Get in touch' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Enable RSS, Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn and enter full url for them. You can uncheck to now show images and links. These images will be show in footer.</li>
		<li>Enter your Address, Phone, Your fax, Your email or select widget 'Footer column 3'.</li>
		<li>Enter Footer copyrigh info.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

<ul><h4>'Footer' options</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Enter first and second testimonial or select widget 'Footer column 1' and 'Footer column 2'.</li>
		<li>Enter your Address, Phone, Your fax, Your email or select widget 'Footer column 3'.</li>
		<li>Enter Footer copyrigh info.</li>
	</ul>
</ul>

